title: Aleksandr Parshin
text:
Aleksandr Gennadyevich Parshin (; born 15 January 1986) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. 
Club career.
He made his debut for <a href="FC%20Shinnik%20Yaroslavl">FC Shinnik Yaroslavl</a> on 2 July 2006 in a <a href="Russian%20Cup%20%28football%29">Russian Cup</a> game against <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Bryansk">FC Dynamo Bryansk</a>.
